          "Name": "Checklist",
          "Type": "field",
          "Offsets": [
            30,
            540,
            92,
            216
          ],
          "Value": "✎ Edit toggles edit mode - drag widgets around, resize them with 8 handles, nudge with arrow keys, snap to a grid\n\nthe properties panel (right) edits every detail; multi-line texts open in a draggable editor window via ⤢\n\n\"+ New\" inserts widgets, \"Card ▾\" manages cards, \"▦ Cards\" shows wireframe thumbnails of the whole deck\n\nundo/redo (Ctrl/Cmd+Z), and copy/paste cards or widgets across decks via the clipboard\n\n📷 downloads a screenshot of the card in its native pixel size",
          "Variant": "transparent",
          "lockText": true,
